g solution what is a postage meter a postage meter weighs and prints postage accurately on your outgoing business mail essentially replacing a stamp postage is downloaded to your meter through your computer or digital telephone line enabling you to pay for your postage without making trips to the post office or keeping piles of stamps in the office you also gain access to usps metered mail discounts   what is an office shipping solution pitney bowes office shipping solutions are designed to help you simplify each phase of shipping through usps® fedex® and ups® for example sendpro™ is our scalable allinone office solution that helps you streamline an increasingly complex shipping process you can compare options weigh packages print shipping labels track shipments and manage carrier expenses from your desktop or existing mailing system   learn more close simplify your everyday office sending mail process mail quickly and accurately all while gaining access to a  cent savings on every letter you send  accurately weigh your envelopes so you will never pay more ship with sendpro you can view and select delivery options for multiple carriers so that you can make the best choice accurately weigh packages and print professional looking shipping labels all in one place track ship through the major carriers including usps and ups and track every delivery status in one place you can even email delivery notifications to senders or recipients   save save  cents on every letter versus buying stamps at the post office and save with usps shipping with sendpro you will gain access to special ups discounts     see how clients are using our solutions case study with mailing heavy hitter and good advice minnesota twins save k every season “if you want to be successful you’ve got to be efficient and this is efficiency the pitney bowes products we have are top notch” josh fallin coordinator office services minnesota twins using a pitney bowes postage meter desai communications saves mone